7:["$","main",null,{"className":"article-page","children":[["$","script",null,{"type":"application/ld+json","dangerouslySetInnerHTML":{"__html":"{\"@context\":\"https://schema.org\",\"@type\":\"BlogPosting\",\"headline\":\"Pray Before You React: A 60-Second Habit for Couples in Conflict\",\"description\":\"The words that come after a pause and a prayer are almost always better than the ones that come before.\",\"datePublished\":\"2026-07-08\",\"mainEntityOfPage\":\"https://bexhearts.com/blog/pray-before-you-react-couples-conflict\",\"author\":{\"@type\":\"Organization\",\"name\":\"Bexhearts\",\"url\":\"https://bexhearts.com\"},\"publisher\":{\"@type\":\"Organization\",\"name\":\"Bexhearts\",\"url\":\"https://bexhearts.com\"}}"}}],["$","article",null,{"className":"article-shell","children":[["$","$L12",null,{"href":"/blog","className":"back-link","children":[["$","svg",null,{"ref":"$undefined","xmlns":"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg","width":24,"height":24,"viewBox":"0 0 24 24","fill":"none","stroke":"currentColor","strokeWidth":2,"strokeLinecap":"round","strokeLinejoin":"round","className":"lucide lucide-arrow-left","aria-hidden":"true","children":[["$","path","1l729n",{"d":"m12 19-7-7 7-7"}],["$","path","x3x0zl",{"d":"M19 12H5"}],"$undefined"]}],"Blog"]}],["$","header",null,{"className":"article-hero","children":[["$","p",null,{"className":"section-kicker","children":"Prayer"}],["$","h1",null,{"children":"Pray Before You React: A 60-Second Habit for Couples in Conflict"}],["$","p",null,{"children":"The words that come after a pause and a prayer are almost always better than the ones that come before."}],["$","div",null,{"className":"article-meta","children":[["$","time",null,{"dateTime":"2026-07-08","children":"2026-07-08"}],["$","span",null,{"children":[4," min read"]}]]}]]}],["$","div",null,{"className":"article-content","children":[["$","section","0",{"children":["$undefined",[["$","p","Most relationship damage does not come from the disagreement itself. It comes from the first ninety seconds after it starts, when both people are reacting instead of responding.",{"children":"Most relationship damage does not come from the disagreement itself. It comes from the first ninety seconds after it starts, when both people are reacting instead of responding."}],["$","p","A sixty-second prayer is long enough to interrupt that reflex and short enough to actually happen. You are not solving the argument in that minute. You are choosing who you want to be inside it.",{"children":"A sixty-second prayer is long enough to interrupt that reflex and short enough to actually happen. You are not solving the argument in that minute. You are choosing who you want to be inside it."}]]]}],["$","section","What the pause actually does",{"children":[["$","h2",null,{"children":"What the pause actually does"}],[["$","p","Naming the moment to God forces you to name it honestly to yourself. It is very hard to pray about a fight and keep pretending you had no part in it.",{"children":"Naming the moment to God forces you to name it honestly to yourself. It is very hard to pray about a fight and keep pretending you had no part in it."}],["$","p","The prayer can be five words: help me love them well. That is enough to change the sentence you say next.",{"children":"The prayer can be five words: help me love them well. That is enough to change the sentence you say next."}]]]}],["$","section","Make it a shared agreement, not a secret technique",{"children":[["$","h2",null,{"children":"Make it a shared agreement, not a secret technique"}],[["$","p","Tell your partner you want to try this, in a calm moment, not mid-fight. A boundary you both agreed to feels like protection; one that appears mid-argument feels like a wall.",{"children":"Tell your partner you want to try this, in a calm moment, not mid-fight. A boundary you both agreed to feels like protection; one that appears mid-argument feels like a wall."}],"$L13"]]}]]}],"$L14","$L15"]}]]}]
