13:["$","p","Couples who practice this in Bexhearts often pair it with a shared boundary like no name-calling, even in the big ones, so the pause has something to land on.",{"children":"Couples who practice this in Bexhearts often pair it with a shared boundary like no name-calling, even in the big ones, so the pause has something to land on."}]
